item.description: It is a pretty small bar so it will be easy to find the Trailblazers. If you are new the Trailblazers or you have not met me you can email me and I can let you know where we will be. Hope to see you there.
item.why: Let's all meet up for some fun trivia at Kelley's Row! Up to six people make a team, however we have had more on one team before. We are doing really well. We always enjoy drinks and appetizers and have a blast everytime.

group.name: Trailblazers- A Seacoast Singles Meetup Group

item.name: Trivia Night at Kelley's Row
